    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🏫 CLSU Live Row Router — v3\n**n8n 2.9.4 | Google Sheets native**\n\n### Concept:\nThis workflow does NOT generate a new file.\nInstead it **writes rows directly into your Google Sheets template**.\n\n### What happens when you add a row to Data Input:\n1. **Trigger fires** — Google Sheets detects the new row\n2. **Validate** — checks the row has a date\n3. **Check the date** — determines which quarter it belongs to\n4. **Route to Q sheet** — appends to Q1/Q2/Q3/Q4 tab automatically\n5. **Append to Monthly** — also writes it into Monthly Report\n6. **Append to Date Range** — also writes it into Date Range tab\n7. **Update Summary** — refreshes SUMIF totals in Summary Report\n\n### Year-End Reset:\nRun the separate Year-End workflow manually on Dec 31.\nIt archives the year, clears all Q data rows, and resets\nyear labels — the template structure is fully preserved.",
        "height": 564,
        "width": 440,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "213f08bd-282f-4869-aabe-7bd9f8d14027",
      "name": "📋 HOW THIS WORKS",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -80,
        -96
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ✅ Setup Steps\n\n**1. Upload your blank template to Google Sheets**\n→ File → Import → your blank xlsx\n→ Copy the Sheet ID from the URL bar\n   (the long string between /d/ and /edit)\n→ Replace ALL instances of YOUR_SHEET_ID below\n\n**2. Data Input tab — Row 4 must be headers:**\n`Date | Type | Item | Quantity | Unit | Price | Amount Paid | Payor | Mode of Payment | OR Number/Billing No. | Date Issued | Issued by | Source`\n\n**3. Q sheet tabs must exist:**\n→ Q1 Report, Q2 Report, Q3 Report, Q4 Report\n→ Row 5 = column headers, Row 6+ = data area\n\n**4. Connect Google Sheets OAuth2 credential**\n→ Credentials → New → Google Sheets OAuth2\n→ Apply to all Sheets nodes\n\n**5. Activate the workflow** (toggle top right)\n→ It will now auto-trigger on every new row",
        "height": 496,
        "width": 440,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "e8a1980b-9e84-4d3c-b679-a3419567753f",
      "name": "🔧 SETUP",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        384,
        -96
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔄 Year-End Reset\n\nAt the end of each year, run the **Year-End Reset** workflow.\n(It's a separate workflow — import it separately.)\n\n**What it does:**\n✅ Archives this year as a Google Sheets copy\n✅ Clears data rows in Q1, Q2, Q3, Q4, Monthly, Date Range\n✅ Updates year labels (e.g., 2025 → 2026)\n✅ Preserves: headers, formulas, formatting, dropdowns\n\n**Result:** Same Sheet becomes next year's live template\nautomatically — no manual reformatting needed.",
        "height": 284,
        "width": 440,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "6a0fd0aa-e79f-4de5-bc28-6b6c2b71a856",
      "name": "🗓️ YEAR-END RESET INFO",
